	<h1 class="title">《火星救援》槽点成真，NASA 研究怎么在火星种土豆</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/73517/small/73517.jpg?1431406847" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">赖江锟 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-23 12:17:59 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19567/medium/19567.jpg?1450843497" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


